Definition: figurative) the act of reforming by the removal of unwanted personnel or practices or conditions
Example: more housecleaning is in store at other accounting firms; many employees were discharged in a general housecleaning by the new owners
Synonyms: reform, noun, communication, figure_of_speech, u, figurative, the, act, of, reforming, by, removal, unwanted, personnel, or, practices, conditions, more, is, in, store, at, other, accounting, firms, many, employees, were, discharged, a, general, new, owners
Category: noun.act
